snippet.title: Munch - Official Release Date Trailer | Ghouls 4 Games
snippet.description: Kill. Eat. Evolve. Take a look at gameplay in this new trailer for Munch, an upcoming dark fantasy action roguelite game where you unleash your inner monster. Devour the Followers of Order, choose your mutations and transform into 12 different monsters each with their own abilities, soundtrack and appetite. Crush the god Ördo to release the Gods of Heavy Metal! Munch will be available on PC on November 24, 2024.
